label: A2B3_oF40_43_b_ab-001
title: Ag$_{2}$O$_{3}$ Structure
comments: This structure is a distortion of the \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B2_cP10_224_d_b-001}{D5$_{5}$ Ag$_{2}$O$_{3}$ structure (A2B3\_cP10\_224\_b\_d)}, although (Standke, 1986) does not seem to be aware of the earlier work.  This is most likely closer to the correct structure for Ag$_{2}$O$_{3}$ than the D5$_{5}$ structure is.
